OL,3,CPeople could be fined #1000 for
OL,4,Cfeeding wildlife in town centre
OL,6,FPeople in Worthing could be find for
OL,7,Ffeeding wildlife, under plans being
OL,8,Flooked at by the borough council.
OL,10,FA four-week public consultation has
OL,11,Fbeen launched, with people businesses
OL,12,Fand visitors being asked to give their
OL,13,Fviews.
OL,15,FWorthing Borough Council says under
OL,16,Fthe plans, people could fined up to
OL,17,F#1,000, for violations.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
