OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772283793
OL,3,CPeople could be fined #1000 for
OL,4,Cfeeding wildlife in town centre
OL,6,FIt added that though feeding wildlife
OL,7,Fis often well-intentioned, unregulated
OL,8,Ffeeding can have unintended
OL,9,Fconsequences for both animals and the
OL,10,Fpublic.
OL,12,FFeeding pigeons in the town centre has
OL,13,Fbeen highlighted as a concern by some
OL,14,Fin the community.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
