FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772283793
OL,3,CPeople could be fined #1000 for
OL,4,Cfeeding wildlife in town centre
OL,6,FThe authority said availability of
OL,7,Feasily accessible food can contribute
OL,8,Fto increased wildlife populations in
OL,9,Fconcentrated areas, and may result in
OL,10,Fincreased fouling, property damage and
OL,11,Fother nuisance behaviours such as
OL,12,Fscavenging in public spaces.
OL,14,FA spokesperson said higher wildlife
OL,15,Factivity can increase the risk of
OL,16,Fdisease transmission to people and
OL,17,Fdomestic animals.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
