OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772283793
OL,3,CPeople could be fined #1000 for
OL,4,Cfeeding wildlife in town centre
OL,6,FThe authority said people should be
OL,7,Fable to enjoy eating lunch or a
OL,8,Fseaside snack - without being
OL,9,Fdisturbed or pestered by wildlife.
OL,11,FCouncillor Rosey Whorlow, Worthing's
OL,12,Fcabinet member for equalities,
OL,13,Finclusion and community safety, said:
OL,14,F"We know that many people feed
OL,15,Fwildlife with the best of intentions,
OL,16,Fbut unregulated feeding in the town
OL,17,Fcentre can have unintended
OL,18,Fconsequences for both animals and the
OL,19,Fwider community.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
