OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772283793
OL,3,CPeople could be fined #1000 for
OL,4,Cfeeding wildlife in town centre
OL,6,F"We have seen an increase in nuisance
OL,7,Fbehaviour, littering and hygiene
OL,8,Fconcerns linked to this issue in
OL,9,Frecent years, and are interested to
OL,10,Fhear the community's opinion on a
OL,11,Fproposed order that could help improve
OL,12,Fthe situation.
OL,14,F"Our priority is to ensure Worthing
OL,15,Fremains a clean, safe and welcoming
OL,16,Ftown centre for everyone, while also
OL,17,Fprotecting the long-term wellbeing of
OL,18,Flocal wildlife. We encourage people to
OL,19,Ftake part and have their say before
OL,20,Fany decision is made."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU|D@VO]
